An OG on all levels. We know what you're thinking---"Denim?? For a chef coat??" You think those jeans look good on you, right? Well, just try the Chuck. He makes anyone look like a BOSS. Go on, get it...you're guaranteed to fall in love with your new favorite coat.

  • Lightweight dark blue Japanese denim
  • 97% cotton 3% spandex
  • Double-breasted
  • No-fuss neodymium magnetic back apron tab
  • Inset double chest pocket
  • 12 buttons
  • Top sititched with a contrasting mellow yellow
  • Mandarin collar
  • Short-sleeve
  • Longer, curved hemline

Use & Care

  • Machine-wash cold
  • Line dry only
  • Due to the deep rich pigment dyes of this garment, bleeding will occur.  Pigment dyes will rub off on hands with repeated handling. The dyes may transfer to other fabrics or upholstery. Please exercise care when use of this garment is in contact with light colored surfaces.  This requires to cold water wash the garment/product at least once prior to use.

Dimensions

  • Available in sizes XS-3XL

column28:
The Frank. It may be a living legend, or possibly just the most updated classic to date. The 2 way stretch in this coat makes you feel like you can work for days in this superstar. It's made with an extremely lightweight cotton and spandex, and finished with classy cloth covered buttons. Don't forget about all of the Lost Car awesomeness- pen and marker pockets in front for easy access, and the signature apron magnet on the back of your neck to keep that pesky thing from bothering you all shift. 

  • 2 way stretch cotton
  • 97% cotton 3% spandex
  • Double-breasted
  • No-fuss neodymium magnetic back apron tab
  • Top stitched with a contrasting light gray
  • Inset double chest pocket
  • 12 cloth covered buttons
  • Mandarin collar
  • Short-sleeve
  • Longer, curved hemline

Use & Care

  • Machine-wash cold, gentle cycle
  • Line dry only, DO NOT USE DRYER (shrinkage will occur)
  • Due to the 3% spandex in the fabric, please use caution when laundering. Care instructions must be followed in order to maintain the integrity of the product. No refunds or exchanges will be made from the disregard of these instructions.

Dimensions

  • Available in sizes XS-5XL
  • Note: This products sizing runs slightly larger.  Please reference the size chart before purchase.

 

Size Chart

Everyone's favorite bib. Back in full force with it's same awesome stretch, and perfect contrast in colors. This super practical bib apron will protect you from the wear and tear of the day. Keep all of your pens, markers, cell (and whatever else you wanna keep with you throughout your shift) right where you need 'em- in any of 9 pockets that come with this dope apron. 

  • 100% Cotton
  • Black & Grey Japanese Denim
  • White contrasting stitch throughout
  • Contrasting gray pockets and straps
  • Adjustable metal neck buckle
  • Double layered chest pockets with 2 optional pen divides
  • 2 front full size pockets
    • 4 additional inset pen pockets
    • 1 additional inset cell phone pocket

Dimensions

Available in Regular Size: 35.5”L X 31”W

 Use & Care

  • Machine-wash cold
  • Line dry
  • Warm iron as needed

The swaggiest one of the bunch! This bad boy is everything you want in a chef coat- complete with both style AND functionality. Made beautifully with a lightweight Japanese denim, and finished off with 12 gunmetal buttons. You can't forget about all of the Lost Car perks- longer front and back panels, pen pockets in the front of your coat for easier access, and of course, a super strong neodymium magnet on your back to keep your apron from creeping up on your neck. Boom.

  • Lightweight black denim 
  • 97% cotton 3% spandex
  • Double-breasted
  • No-fuss neodymium magnetic back apron tab
  • Inset double chest pocket (both sides- whether your right or left-handed)
  • 12 gunmetal buttons
  • Top stitched with a contrasting gray
  • 1" contrasting striped cuff on the sleeve
  • Mandarin collar
  • Short-sleeve
  • Longer, curved hemline

 Use & Care

  • Machine-wash cold
  • Line dry only

Dimensions

  • Available in sizes XS-3XL
